# Assets Insurance Contractual Regular Contributions Gross Reinsured Amount

## identifier
de4798

## type
float

## definition
Report the total of all Contractual Regular Contributions that have been reinsured as at the relevant date. These are the total gross premiums that are accepted through direct debit, have a specific contractual requirement for future on-going premiums, have an expectation of renewal each year (e.g. Yearly Renewable term products) or generally cause a policy to discontinue on cessation of future payment.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Assets.Insurance.ContractualRegularContributionsGrossReinsured.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.04
- period=instant
